{"tid":2219171,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《彼得潘》小仙子選角確定　「20歲黑人女星」演出　","createTime":"2020-09-26T16:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T07:14:35.000Z","uid":10830,"like":3,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"82fb14ffe1e2efb3a10c6b447521eaffcf83745f","tid":2219171,"uid":10830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"記者蕭采薇／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼電影《小美人魚》（The Little Mermaid）真人版，在去年七月宣布由黑人女星荷莉貝利（Halle Bailey）演出女主角愛麗兒，當時就引發「過度政治正確」的爭議。事隔一年，迪士尼沒有受到輿論影響，26日再度宣佈旗下另一個經典的「白皮膚」角色，將再次由黑人女星演出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5166/d5166489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5166%2Fd5166489.jpg&h=0f753237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼黑人女星亞拉沙希迪（Yara Shahidi）接演《彼得潘》小叮噹（Tinker Bell）。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n▲《彼得潘》仙子「小叮噹」（Tinker Bell）雖不是主角，但是重要的經典角色。（圖／劇照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5166/d5166492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5166%2Fd5166492.jpg&h=45643a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迪士尼決定將經典動畫《彼得潘》（Peter Pan，前譯：小飛俠）再度真人化，推出電影《彼得潘與溫蒂》（Peter Pan＆Wendy），經典角色「精靈」小叮噹（Tinker Bell）一度傳出將由「小丑女」瑪格羅比（Margot Robbie）飾演，不過26日官方宣布，將由20歲黑人女星亞拉沙希迪（Yara Shahidi）演出。<br />\n<br />\n小叮噹動畫中形象是金髮、白膚、紅唇和藍眼睛的小仙子，迪士尼在《小美人魚》愛麗兒後，再度起用黑人女星演出經典的「白皮膚」角色，不難看出迪士尼想打破膚色刻板印象的決心。雖然有認為「過度政治正確」的聲音，但也有人認為：「要批評也等看到作品再說。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5166/d5166488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5166%2Fd5166488.jpg&h=c3df32a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亞拉沙希迪尚未對此表達意見，不過先前她曾力挺荷莉貝利接演《小美人魚》愛麗兒，當時亞拉表示：「我認為她的確保留了愛麗兒所有經典特質，同時也帶著獨特的自信和能力，當您聽到她的聲音時，會知道一切都很完美。」<br />\n<br />\n電影《彼得潘與溫蒂》將由裘德洛（Jude Law）飾演虎克船長、亞歷山大莫洛尼（Alexander Molony）飾演彼得潘、艾薇安德森（Ever Anderson）飾演溫蒂。導演則為大衛洛瑞（David Lowery），本片開拍時間尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4676/d4676506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4676%2Fd4676506.jpg&h=399d4410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「小叮噹」一度傳出將由瑪格羅比接演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0b82e84b67c6567a6f63288e708feab3af5c37","tid":2219171,"uid":61954,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"求其啦<br />\n反正花木蘭之後<br />\n正常人都唔會再對迪士尼啲動畫改編戲抱有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd75db68a6341edd8269ea688c3084036cd8a026","tid":2219171,"uid":10830,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"小美人魚又係咁<br />\n小仙子又係咁<br />\n迪士尼我屌你老母啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94789567aa76b9ecdcb06a8fca6570019fc5a77","tid":2219171,"uid":162095,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"改篇黑人角色比白人做=racist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgm